   "source": [
    "# Python换源"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 临时换源"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "可以在使用pip的时候在后面加上-i参数，指定pip源\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "pip install scrapy -i https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 永久换源"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "永久修改：\n",
    "linux:\n",
    "修改 ~/.pip/pip.conf (没有就创建一个)， 内容如下：\n",
    "```python\n",
    "[global]\n",
    "index-url = https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple\n",
    "```"
   ]
  }
 ],
